extendedInfo.description: Listen online streams of  electronic music live DJ sets, Promo Mixes, Podcast and Radio Show recordings. Download free the ones you like. All our content is free and legal to use.The new mobile application provided by Killing Beats Dot Com.The DJ shows, sets  and mixes are being updated as soon as they are aired on the relevant radio station or being released by the DJs.This application for DJ sets streaming is tested in a car moving with over 100 km/h (60 mph) all the DJ sets are streamed flawless.Here's short list the available and frequently updated DJ shows.
